UnstakeTokensViaAdapter_Integration_Concrete_Test
├── given null
│  └── it should revert
└── given not null
   ├── given no adapter
   │  └── it should revert
   └── given adapter
      ├── given already unstaked
      │  └── it should revert
      └── given not unstaked
         ├── given yield token balance zero
         │  └── it should revert
         └── given yield token balance not zero
            ├── given active
            │  ├── when sync does not change status
            │  │  └── it should revert
            │  └── when sync changes status
            │     ├── it should sync price from oracle
            │     ├── it should return the amount received from the adapter
            │     ├── it should transfer tokens back to Bob
            │     ├── it should mark the vault as unstaked
            │     └── it should emit {SyncPriceFromOracle}, {UnstakeFromAdapter} and {UnstakeFullAmount} events
            └── given not active
               ├── when slippage exceeds tolerance
               │  └── it should revert
               └── when slippage not exceed tolerance
                  ├── it should return the amount received from the adapter
                  ├── it should transfer tokens back to Bob
                  ├── it should mark the vault as unstaked
                  └── it should emit {UnstakeFromAdapter} and {UnstakeFullAmount} events
